	(tgba_succ_iterator_concrete::next): Use nownext_set to simplify.

	Rewrite tgba_succ_iterator_concrete::next for the fourth time
	(or is it the fifth?).

	* src/tgba/succiterconcrete.hh
	(tgba_succ_iterator_concrete::trans_dest_,
